{"tid":925807,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【母殺親兒】淹死5歲子再斬頭放膠袋 媽棄親兒屍於垃圾桶","createTime":"2018-12-03T04:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T04:15:23.000Z","uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"47ff52cec73c9db87a513e18dd98a0141faf1797","tid":925807,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181203/large/1543795031_d51e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181203%2Flarge%2F1543795031_d51e.jpg&h=bcda3359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姓劉女子承認殺子，被控謀殺。<br />\n美國德州侯斯頓一名女子涉嫌將5歲兒子淹死後，斬去兒子頭顱後將屍體棄於垃圾桶。<br />\n警方表示，43歲譯音姓劉（Lihui Liu）的女子，上周五懷疑在浴室殘殺兒子後棄屍。丈夫放工回家，劉告訴對方已把兒子趕走，丈夫四處尋找兒子之際，劉最終承認兒子在車房外的垃圾桶內。他發現兒子的屍體及頭顱在垃圾桶內以黑膠袋包住。<br />\n警方接報有斬人案後到劉的寓所調查，在浴室發現兇器，浴缸血迹斑斑。劉當場被捕，承認將兒子淹斃，已被控謀殺。劉與丈夫還育有13歲女兒，未知案發時她是否在屋內。<br />\n美國《紐約郵報》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181203/58985243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181203%2F58985243&d=JdofEqXGygwe9bBNhTug2kzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=8842e8a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181203%2F58985243&h=381d0db5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181203/58985243</a>"},{"pid":"3ab760f8ee6ccd5408f5777992b2ec9d6a87b523","tid":925807,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88626ec951d651e3933f91a18da59fdcda4acfb9","tid":925807,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:09:00.000Z","msg":"用酷刑啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cfee721a89d7a5de38fd